WEBVTT

00:02:19.960 --> 00:02:20.919
What about you?

00:02:21.240 --> 00:02:22.360
And don't try to talk me out of it.

00:02:22.879 --> 00:02:24.120
Anyway, regarding Master Sun,

00:02:24.240 --> 00:02:25.280
I'm definitely hiring him.

00:02:26.599 --> 00:02:29.240
Wait, let's put the Master Sun matter aside for now.

00:02:29.800 --> 00:02:31.840
I went back and thought it over carefully.

00:02:32.560 --> 00:02:34.800
Actually, our voting mechanism

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:35.960
has a bit of a problem.

00:02:36.560 --> 00:02:39.240
It always ends in a two-to-two tie, right?

00:02:39.400 --> 00:02:40.759
So I was thinking,

00:02:41.159 --> 00:02:43.960
we could bring in a new shareholder.

00:02:46.759 --> 00:02:48.439
I agree too.

00:02:50.919 --> 00:02:53.080
Who are you guys thinking of?

00:02:53.360 --> 00:02:54.199
Big Brother.

00:02:55.080 --> 00:02:57.199
You can't just add a shareholder casually.

00:02:57.360 --> 00:02:59.000
Of course not casually.

00:02:59.319 --> 00:03:01.560
If you disagree with the new candidate,

00:03:01.599 --> 00:03:04.159
then we can put it to a vote.

00:03:16.919 --> 00:03:17.759
Wait.

00:03:18.199 --> 00:03:20.759
You're not bringing *him* back, are you?

00:03:21.759 --> 00:03:22.360
See?

00:03:22.520 --> 00:03:25.000
I told you Second Brother is sharp as a tack.

00:03:25.000 --> 00:03:25.879
I think so too.

00:03:25.879 --> 00:03:27.360
Second Brother really is sharp.

00:03:27.360 --> 00:03:28.560
I think if we vote again,

00:03:28.560 --> 00:03:30.039
we should also hear Sister-in-law's opinion.

00:03:31.719 --> 00:03:33.159
Who are you talking about?

00:03:35.039 --> 00:03:37.000
Weiguo. Come on in.

00:03:40.360 --> 00:03:43.439
Then this time, my vote goes to Weiguo.

00:03:47.439 --> 00:03:48.439
Well, well.

00:03:48.960 --> 00:03:50.560
You've learned to stage a coup.

00:03:52.960 --> 00:03:54.840
Big Brother and Qiu'er both came to beg me.

00:03:54.840 --> 00:03:56.840
I couldn't just refuse them, could I?

00:03:57.840 --> 00:03:58.560
Come on, come on.

00:03:58.560 --> 00:03:59.840
Sit, sit, sit.

00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:00.840
Come on.

00:04:00.840 --> 00:04:03.039
Second Brother, Second Brother, you sit here.

00:04:03.039 --> 00:04:03.879
Sit with your Big Brother.

00:04:03.879 --> 00:04:04.560
Right next to your Big Brother.

00:04:04.560 --> 00:04:05.319
Sit down, sit down.

00:04:05.319 --> 00:04:06.560
Yes, yes, come over here.

00:04:06.560 --> 00:04:07.759
Sit next to your Big Brother.

00:04:09.719 --> 00:04:10.719
Sister-in-law, you sit.

00:04:14.879 --> 00:04:16.000
How can I do that?

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:16.759
I've already bought my ticket.

00:04:16.759 --> 00:04:17.839
I'm leaving the day after tomorrow.

00:04:18.040 --> 00:04:19.319
Just return the ticket.

00:04:20.480 --> 00:04:21.720
I'll cover the service fee.

00:04:21.720 --> 00:04:22.439
Alright?

00:04:22.439 --> 00:04:23.480
That doesn't seem right.

00:04:23.560 --> 00:04:24.759
What do you mean, doesn't seem right?

00:04:24.759 --> 00:04:26.720
Having a home and not returning to it, *that's* not right.

00:04:28.319 --> 00:04:29.160
Weiguo.

00:04:30.279 --> 00:04:31.720
I want you to stay.

00:04:31.720 --> 00:04:32.879
No other meaning behind it.

00:04:33.279 --> 00:04:34.319
I just feel

00:04:34.319 --> 00:04:36.319
the four of us brothers started this business together.

00:04:36.319 --> 00:04:38.279
Let's build Peng Le Xuan back up again.

00:04:38.560 --> 00:04:39.879
Let's not have anyone missing.

00:04:39.879 --> 00:04:41.720
Right, no one missing, no one.

00:04:42.879 --> 00:04:44.120
Big Brother, Qiu'er.

00:04:44.279 --> 00:04:45.040
Think about it.

00:04:45.199 --> 00:04:47.439
Before, I was the one putting up money to invest.

00:04:47.439 --> 00:04:48.600
I still had a say.

00:04:48.600 --> 00:04:49.720
But look at me now...

00:04:49.720 --> 00:04:50.519
Right? I...

00:04:52.959 --> 00:04:54.160
Weiguo, here's the deal.

00:04:54.639 --> 00:04:56.319
As long as you're willing to stay,

00:04:56.560 --> 00:04:58.639
the veto power is still yours.

00:04:58.800 --> 00:04:59.399
Right.

00:04:59.399 --> 00:05:01.319
We'll follow your lead, Ma Weiguo.

00:05:04.199 --> 00:05:05.079
Alright then.

00:05:05.079 --> 00:05:07.199
Since Big Brother and Qiu'er have gone this far,

00:05:07.360 --> 00:05:08.639
I'll reluctantly agree.

00:05:12.319 --> 00:05:13.199
So exhausting.

00:05:13.199 --> 00:05:15.639
Oh, now you're getting carried away.

00:05:18.079 --> 00:05:19.199
I propose,

00:05:19.680 --> 00:05:21.040
formally propose,

00:05:21.040 --> 00:05:22.279
that this Ma Weiguo

00:05:22.279 --> 00:05:25.720
joins our Peng Le Xuan Catering Co., Ltd.

00:05:25.720 --> 00:05:27.519
as the Operations Director,

00:05:27.519 --> 00:05:29.839
and enjoys veto power.

00:05:30.720 --> 00:05:32.120
If anyone disagrees,

00:05:32.120 --> 00:05:33.639
we'll take a vote.

00:05:33.800 --> 00:05:34.720
We'll... we'll vote.

00:05:34.720 --> 00:05:35.959
What's the point of voting now?

00:05:36.600 --> 00:05:38.680
Didn't Sister-in-law just state her position?

00:05:39.360 --> 00:05:41.399
Look, Second Brother, the way you talk.

00:05:41.399 --> 00:05:42.839
We need Weiguo back, don't we?

00:05:42.839 --> 00:05:44.839
Since you've all already decided,

00:05:45.319 --> 00:05:47.000
my opposition is meaningless.

00:05:48.360 --> 00:05:49.959
But you'd better all think clearly.

00:05:51.480 --> 00:05:53.560
You all know what kind of person Ma Weiguo is.

00:05:53.720 --> 00:05:55.759
When he turns around and bites you hard later,

00:05:55.959 --> 00:05:57.399
don't come crying about the pain.

00:05:57.839 --> 00:05:58.839
No way, no way.

00:05:58.839 --> 00:06:00.160
It won't come to that.

00:06:00.279 --> 00:06:03.279
Fine. Since everyone agrees,

00:06:03.600 --> 00:06:04.959
let's put what we just discussed

00:06:04.959 --> 00:06:06.279
into a contract.

00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:07.839
Black and white.

00:06:07.839 --> 00:06:09.279
To avoid any disputes later.

00:06:09.519 --> 00:06:09.920
Right.

00:06:09.920 --> 00:06:10.959
Is that really necessary?

00:06:11.279 --> 00:06:12.920
We're running a serious business, right?

00:06:12.920 --> 00:06:15.120
There should always be a formal procedure.

00:06:15.839 --> 00:06:16.519
Right.

00:06:30.079 --> 00:06:30.920
Look.

00:06:31.720 --> 00:06:32.279
Here.

00:06:36.279 --> 00:06:37.279
Come on, Second Brother.

00:06:37.839 --> 00:06:39.480
Sign it. Come on.

00:06:41.439 --> 00:06:42.839
Fine, I'll sign.

00:06:45.319 --> 00:06:46.720
The smell of conspiracy now

00:06:46.720 --> 00:06:48.279
is getting stronger and stronger.

00:06:50.399 --> 00:06:51.160
Weiguo.

00:06:51.399 --> 00:06:52.600
In the future, if there's anything,

00:06:52.600 --> 00:06:54.040
you can also say it in the group chat.

00:07:00.800 --> 00:07:02.920
Alright, that Weiguo

00:07:02.920 --> 00:07:05.079
Then you'll have a tough road ahead.

00:07:05.560 --> 00:07:06.120
Here.

00:07:06.680 --> 00:07:07.839
Don't worry, Big Brother.

00:07:07.920 --> 00:07:10.040
I'm here to solve problems.

00:07:10.480 --> 00:07:11.240
Don't worry.

00:07:13.639 --> 00:07:14.680
Let's take it step by step.

00:07:14.879 --> 00:07:16.639
They say even brothers should keep clear accounts.

00:07:16.959 --> 00:07:18.079
Qiu'er drafted something earlier.

00:07:18.079 --> 00:07:19.399
A shareholder agreement.

00:07:19.399 --> 00:07:20.720
I've revised and improved a few points.

00:07:20.720 --> 00:07:22.040
Let's sign this first.

00:07:22.519 --> 00:07:23.439
As for me, I just...

00:07:23.439 --> 00:07:24.519
drafted a...

00:07:24.759 --> 00:07:26.519
agreement. Take a look first.

00:07:27.040 --> 00:07:27.519
You...

00:07:27.519 --> 00:07:30.279
After all, I can't just take the profits for free.

00:07:30.279 --> 00:07:32.319
In the shareholder rights section,

00:07:32.319 --> 00:07:34.000
I've also written my due obligations.

00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:36.279
I just think before our investor arrives,

00:07:36.279 --> 00:07:37.839
we should get this settled first.

00:07:37.839 --> 00:07:40.120
You all look too, see if anything needs adding.

00:07:41.759 --> 00:07:43.560
No one said you were taking it for free.

00:07:44.680 --> 00:07:45.959
Are you worried

00:07:45.959 --> 00:07:47.680
you won't get that five percent stake?

00:07:47.759 --> 00:07:48.519
No way.

00:07:48.519 --> 00:07:50.759
I just think it's more standard to put it on paper.

00:07:50.759 --> 00:07:52.800
For the sake of our operational standards.

00:07:52.800 --> 00:07:53.519
What do you think?

00:07:53.519 --> 00:07:54.199
Qiu'er.

00:07:54.560 --> 00:07:57.120
You said for the four of us brothers to do this together,

00:07:57.600 --> 00:07:58.519
I didn't hesitate at all.

00:07:58.519 --> 00:07:59.399
I even brought out the shop.

00:07:59.399 --> 00:07:59.680
Right.

00:07:59.680 --> 00:08:02.199
Why would I sign this with you?

00:08:02.199 --> 00:08:03.959
Bro, don't be so casual about it.

00:08:04.120 --> 00:08:04.839
Here's the thing.

00:08:04.839 --> 00:08:06.399
I've seen how bank accounts with hundreds of millions

00:08:06.399 --> 00:08:07.800
are handled.

00:08:07.800 --> 00:08:09.079
I'm really doing this for everyone's good.

00:08:09.079 --> 00:08:09.839
Let's just operate

00:08:09.839 --> 00:08:11.279
properly and formally, okay?

00:08:11.279 --> 00:08:12.120
Be a bit more standard.

00:08:12.240 --> 00:08:13.519
Look, look.

00:08:17.959 --> 00:08:19.480
Last signature.

00:08:19.480 --> 00:08:20.519
Weiguo, have some water.

00:08:20.519 --> 00:08:21.279
Thanks, Sister-in-law.

00:08:23.519 --> 00:08:24.279
All signed, Qiu'er.

00:08:24.279 --> 00:08:24.680
Good.

00:08:25.079 --> 00:08:26.839
Now that everyone's signed,

00:08:27.079 --> 00:08:28.519
let me say a few things.

00:08:28.720 --> 00:08:29.399
Go ahead.

00:08:30.879 --> 00:08:32.879
Let's start with the simple questions.

00:08:33.039 --> 00:08:33.720
Alright.

00:08:34.000 --> 00:08:34.639
Qiu'er.

00:08:35.679 --> 00:08:37.000
You're getting five percent for free.

00:08:38.279 --> 00:08:40.720
You take dividends but still work for the bank.

00:08:40.919 --> 00:08:43.039
What tangible contribution do you make to the company?

00:08:43.519 --> 00:08:44.960
Why should you get PR funds?

00:08:44.960 --> 00:08:46.120
Why should you get reimbursements?

00:08:46.360 --> 00:08:47.639
Why should you draw a salary?

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:50.320
Weiguo, what are you talking about?

00:08:51.159 --> 00:08:52.840
Since Peng Le Xuan opened,

00:08:52.879 --> 00:08:54.320
you haven't accomplished anything.

00:08:54.519 --> 00:08:56.639
Told to bring in clients, you failed.

00:08:56.879 --> 00:08:59.000
Li Lianbao told you to quit your bank job

00:08:59.000 --> 00:09:00.120
and focus on the venture.

00:09:00.120 --> 00:09:02.159
You didn't listen, made endless excuses.

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:04.360
You kept telling me you'd work hard.

00:09:04.639 --> 00:09:05.840
Are you really trying?

00:09:06.159 --> 00:09:07.519
You're just acting like you're trying.

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:12.279
I never said I wouldn't quit.

00:09:12.639 --> 00:09:14.399
Doesn't it need a process?

00:09:14.480 --> 00:09:15.120
Fine.

00:09:15.279 --> 00:09:16.679
Then I'll respect your process.

00:09:18.120 --> 00:09:19.120
First proposal.

00:09:19.519 --> 00:09:22.399
Cancel all of Tong Qiu's benefits in this company

00:09:22.679 --> 00:09:25.120
until he quits his bank job.

00:09:25.399 --> 00:09:27.399
Hold on, Weiguo, look...

00:09:27.639 --> 00:09:28.639
Let's let Qiu'er

00:09:28.639 --> 00:09:30.759
earn some money there first,

00:09:30.759 --> 00:09:32.279
and then talk about it, okay?

00:09:33.240 --> 00:09:34.000
Whose side are you on?

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:35.120
Your big brother is right.

00:09:35.559 --> 00:09:37.679
Why stab me in the back first?

00:09:38.159 --> 00:09:39.720
I'm on Peng Le Xuan's side.

00:09:39.919 --> 00:09:41.879
I support anything good for Peng Le Xuan.

00:09:41.879 --> 00:09:42.759
I back it.

00:09:42.919 --> 00:09:45.120
I oppose anything bad for Peng Le Xuan.

00:09:45.120 --> 00:09:46.120
Am I wrong?

00:09:48.799 --> 00:09:50.120
No, Qiu'er, later...

00:09:50.120 --> 00:09:50.519
Big Brother.

00:09:50.519 --> 00:09:51.399
I and that...

00:09:52.639 --> 00:09:53.960
Next is your problem.

00:09:58.120 --> 00:10:00.200
Wha... it's my turn already?

00:10:00.639 --> 00:10:02.120
What... what's my problem?

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:04.759
Do you think

00:10:05.320 --> 00:10:07.159
you have what it takes to be Chairman?

00:10:07.639 --> 00:10:08.639
You...

00:10:09.279 --> 00:10:10.639
Just because you're the eldest brother?

00:10:11.080 --> 00:10:11.759
Right?

00:10:12.279 --> 00:10:14.120
Is business a place for seniority

00:10:14.120 --> 00:10:15.600
and sentiment?

00:10:16.240 --> 00:10:16.960
Let me ask you.

00:10:17.279 --> 00:10:19.399
The company has over ten million in the account now.

00:10:19.799 --> 00:10:20.679
How will you use it?

00:10:20.879 --> 00:10:22.159
Can you tell me clearly?

00:10:22.279 --> 00:10:22.879
Here's the thing.

00:10:22.879 --> 00:10:23.840
A person

00:10:24.279 --> 00:10:25.759
needs to know their place.

00:10:26.000 --> 00:10:27.759
Peng Le Xuan is a century-old brand.

00:10:27.919 --> 00:10:29.679
It must produce the ancestral flavor.

00:10:29.799 --> 00:10:30.960
Your primary duty

00:10:31.360 --> 00:10:32.480
is to be the chef.

00:10:33.360 --> 00:10:34.120
Proposal two.

00:10:35.279 --> 00:10:38.000
Remove Big Brother from the Chairman position.

00:10:38.279 --> 00:10:39.519
He remains a shareholder.

00:10:39.679 --> 00:10:41.399
Focus on honing his craft from now on.

00:10:41.399 --> 00:10:42.879
Apart from roast duck matters,

00:10:43.159 --> 00:10:44.320
he can do nothing else.

00:10:46.840 --> 00:10:48.200
Ma Weiguo, you're amazing.

00:10:50.240 --> 00:10:51.720
I'll toast you.

00:10:55.039 --> 00:10:55.879
Chunsheng.

00:10:57.159 --> 00:10:58.879
Weiguo, this isn't right, I'm telling you.

00:10:58.879 --> 00:11:00.639
How did you come back like this?

00:11:00.799 --> 00:11:02.600
Chunsheng, you... stop, stop.

00:11:03.360 --> 00:11:06.000
What are you doing? You're crazy.

00:11:07.440 --> 00:11:09.679
So, is it my turn next?

00:11:11.799 --> 00:11:12.559
You.

00:11:13.440 --> 00:11:15.279
You are just too soft-hearted

00:11:15.279 --> 00:11:16.519
towards Big Brother and Qiu'er.

00:11:17.440 --> 00:11:18.519
Other than that,

00:11:19.000 --> 00:11:20.200
I think you've done alright.

00:11:21.399 --> 00:11:22.399
Thank you.

00:11:22.759 --> 00:11:24.519
That's my highest praise for you.

00:11:24.960 --> 00:11:25.919
However,

00:11:26.200 --> 00:11:27.639
the way you sidelined Big Brother,

00:11:27.639 --> 00:11:29.120
cutting off all family ties,

00:11:29.480 --> 00:11:30.679
makes me quite respect you.

00:11:31.639 --> 00:11:32.639
Funny.

00:11:33.519 --> 00:11:35.519
The way you used Big Brother and Qiu'er

00:11:35.519 --> 00:11:37.399
and then slit their carotid artery in return,

00:11:37.840 --> 00:11:40.440
that move also makes me respect you.

00:11:41.440 --> 00:11:42.279
Impressive.

00:11:42.799 --> 00:11:44.039
You're the impressive one.

00:11:51.399 --> 00:11:52.759
Honey, slow down.

00:11:52.759 --> 00:11:55.000
What are you so angry about?

00:11:55.279 --> 00:11:57.159
Big Brother, Big Brother.

00:11:57.279 --> 00:11:58.120
I don't think that's right.

00:11:58.240 --> 00:11:59.519
We need to have a word with him.

00:11:59.519 --> 00:12:01.000
What's there to talk about?

00:12:01.279 --> 00:12:02.759
Qiu'er, let me tell you something.

00:12:03.000 --> 00:12:03.879
From now on,

00:12:03.879 --> 00:12:05.120
don't call me Big Brother anymore.

00:12:05.120 --> 00:12:06.639
I'm not worthy.

00:12:06.759 --> 00:12:08.000
I'm an embarrassment.

00:12:08.000 --> 00:12:09.279
What are you talking about?

00:12:09.519 --> 00:12:10.639
Honey, look at you getting so worked up

00:12:10.639 --> 00:12:11.759
over him.

00:12:11.759 --> 00:12:13.320
It's just not worth it.

00:12:13.639 --> 00:12:14.279
No, but listen to him.

00:12:14.279 --> 00:12:16.000
Did you hear what he just said?

00:12:16.000 --> 00:12:18.399
What does he mean, "I need to know my place"?

00:12:18.519 --> 00:12:19.639
Let me tell you all something.

00:12:19.759 --> 00:12:21.879
I never wanted to be this Chairman in the first place.

00:12:21.879 --> 00:12:22.519
Right?

00:12:22.759 --> 00:12:24.759
But you can't just push me around like that.

00:12:24.759 --> 00:12:25.120
Yes, yes, yes.

00:12:25.120 --> 00:12:25.879
Right? I mean,

00:12:25.879 --> 00:12:26.879
he said he was leaving.

00:12:27.279 --> 00:12:29.639
I rushed over to deliver money to him.

00:12:29.639 --> 00:12:30.120
Right?

00:12:30.120 --> 00:12:31.120
I even pulled him in

00:12:31.120 --> 00:12:32.879
to work on Peng Le Xuan with us.

00:12:33.320 --> 00:12:35.600
I'm just a big fool.

00:12:36.320 --> 00:12:37.840
Slow down, mind your back.

00:12:42.600 --> 00:12:43.679
You know me,

00:12:44.320 --> 00:12:45.799
I don't give up that easily.

00:12:47.159 --> 00:12:49.120
The three months aren't up yet.

00:12:50.080 --> 00:12:51.879
Right now, there's a perfect opportunity.

00:12:52.480 --> 00:12:53.720
If we seize it,

00:12:54.519 --> 00:12:56.279
Peng Le Xuan can take off quickly.

00:12:58.279 --> 00:12:59.519
The Duck King competition.

00:12:59.679 --> 00:13:00.399
Exactly.

00:13:01.559 --> 00:13:02.559
I've looked into it.

00:13:03.080 --> 00:13:05.279
This competition is different from others.

00:13:05.440 --> 00:13:06.919
It's not all flashy.

00:13:07.559 --> 00:13:08.679
It's simple.

00:13:09.120 --> 00:13:10.919
But also professional.

00:13:11.399 --> 00:13:12.639
Within the industry,

00:13:12.639 --> 00:13:14.120
it carries some authority.

00:13:15.559 --> 00:13:17.399
If Big Brother wants to stand out

00:13:17.399 --> 00:13:18.759
in this competition,

00:13:19.080 --> 00:13:21.080
he must regain his old skills.

00:13:21.879 --> 00:13:24.360
Rediscover Peng Le Xuan's unique flavor.

00:13:26.720 --> 00:13:28.759
There are only a few days left until the competition.

00:13:29.080 --> 00:13:30.480
By the time Big Brother recovers his skills,

00:13:30.679 --> 00:13:32.039
it'll be too late.

00:13:35.240 --> 00:13:36.440
Think it through carefully.

00:13:37.039 --> 00:13:38.240
This competition

00:13:38.519 --> 00:13:39.559
cannot be lost.

00:13:40.399 --> 00:13:41.159
By the way,

00:13:41.600 --> 00:13:44.200
do you know who Li Lianbao got the money from?

00:13:46.440 --> 00:13:47.159
Kevin.

00:13:49.639 --> 00:13:51.240
He really knows how to adapt.

00:13:52.279 --> 00:13:53.519
And Kevin's

00:13:53.759 --> 00:13:55.639
investment terms are very harsh.

00:13:55.960 --> 00:13:56.919
Within six months,

00:13:56.919 --> 00:13:58.039
Peng Le Xuan must be pushed

00:13:58.039 --> 00:14:00.279
into the top ten rankings on all platforms.

00:14:00.639 --> 00:14:02.639
Otherwise, not only will future investments stop,

00:14:02.639 --> 00:14:04.159
but even the initial investment funds

00:14:04.159 --> 00:14:05.639
must all be returned.

00:14:07.279 --> 00:14:08.519
As far as I know,

00:14:08.600 --> 00:14:10.600
Big Brother and Qiu'er don't know about this condition.

00:14:11.639 --> 00:14:14.159
He hasn't told anyone about this.

00:14:14.159 --> 00:14:15.440
He's bearing it all himself.

00:14:16.039 --> 00:14:18.279
So, using this point,

00:14:18.799 --> 00:14:21.279
as long as we severely hinder Peng Le Xuan's development,

00:14:21.759 --> 00:14:22.720
very soon,

00:14:23.039 --> 00:14:24.679
Li Lianbao himself won't be able to hold on.

00:14:26.279 --> 00:14:27.799
This is also his fatal weakness.

00:14:37.039 --> 00:14:38.799
We are definitely going to the competition.

00:14:39.279 --> 00:14:40.840
But as for who goes...

00:14:41.159 --> 00:14:42.159
that's a secret for now.

00:14:43.440 --> 00:14:44.840
I strongly suggest

00:14:45.200 --> 00:14:46.559
that Big Brother competes.

00:14:46.759 --> 00:14:48.080
Steady and sure.

00:14:48.559 --> 00:14:49.679
Don't rush for quick success.

00:14:50.039 --> 00:14:51.240
I firmly disagree.

00:14:52.039 --> 00:14:54.080
Speed is our top priority right now.

00:14:54.720 --> 00:14:55.759
Only speed can break through.

00:14:57.519 --> 00:14:58.720
Let's agree to disagree.

00:15:05.639 --> 00:15:06.639
The wind is about to pick up.

00:15:08.879 --> 00:15:11.200
This time is different from before.

00:15:12.919 --> 00:15:14.320
Get ready to grow wings.

00:15:16.960 --> 00:15:18.200
What nonsense.

00:15:19.759 --> 00:15:20.919
Are you crazy?

00:15:33.559 --> 00:15:34.320
Old Liu,

00:15:34.720 --> 00:15:36.159
I have something big to tell you.

00:15:37.159 --> 00:15:37.919
Just now,

00:15:37.919 --> 00:15:40.399
Ma Weiguo said I'm going to grow wings.

00:15:41.159 --> 00:15:43.519
I'm preparing to go against the wind.

00:15:43.600 --> 00:15:45.120
We're about to take off.

00:15:47.279 --> 00:15:48.519
Yes, yes, yes.

00:15:49.960 --> 00:15:50.840
So,

00:15:51.159 --> 00:15:54.200
this Duck King competition,

00:15:54.399 --> 00:15:55.919
we must place.

00:15:56.519 --> 00:15:58.279
And it must be the championship.

00:15:59.399 --> 00:16:01.799
After winning, our Peng Le Xuan will take off.

00:16:03.120 --> 00:16:05.600
We must be number one in the capital.

00:16:12.919 --> 00:16:14.399
You've been lying here all day.

00:16:14.399 --> 00:16:16.320
It's time to eat, you need to eat.

00:16:20.159 --> 00:16:21.679
Come on, let me see.

00:16:22.799 --> 00:16:23.799
What's wrong?

00:16:24.039 --> 00:16:24.919
Let me feel.

00:16:32.360 --> 00:16:34.559
No fever either.

00:16:35.519 --> 00:16:36.639
Get up and have a bite.

00:16:36.799 --> 00:16:37.399
Listen,

00:16:37.399 --> 00:16:38.919
you love chives, right?

00:16:38.919 --> 00:16:41.399
Look, I made chives with shrimp for you today.

00:16:41.399 --> 00:16:41.799
No, I mean...

00:16:41.799 --> 00:16:42.480
It's super fragrant.

00:16:42.480 --> 00:16:44.039
I'm... I'm not hungry.

00:16:44.039 --> 00:16:45.519
If you don't want to be in the living room,

00:16:45.519 --> 00:16:47.039
you can eat in the room, okay?

00:16:49.600 --> 00:16:52.200
Dad, you've been lying down all day.

00:16:53.080 --> 00:16:54.320
Get up and move around.

00:17:00.120 --> 00:17:01.600
How about I go for a run downstairs,

00:17:01.600 --> 00:17:03.399
and you ride your bike to keep me company?

00:17:03.399 --> 00:17:05.279
Yes, come on, go for a walk with your son.

00:17:05.279 --> 00:17:06.880
You, you need to move.

00:17:06.880 --> 00:17:07.799
You've been cooped up all day.

00:17:07.799 --> 00:17:09.119
Even your own farts would stink you out.

00:17:09.119 --> 00:17:09.759
Go on.

00:17:12.759 --> 00:17:14.799
What did you promise Third Uncle back then?

00:17:15.160 --> 00:17:15.920
Didn't you agree

00:17:15.920 --> 00:17:17.039
to set a good example for me?

00:17:17.039 --> 00:17:18.519
Don't mention Ma Weiguo to me.

00:17:19.519 --> 00:17:20.920
No, I'm just not hungry.

00:17:20.920 --> 00:17:23.200
You two go ahead and eat.

00:17:29.519 --> 00:17:30.359
Go on, go.

00:17:33.640 --> 00:17:34.799
Close the door.

00:17:51.920 --> 00:17:52.440
Mom

00:17:53.200 --> 00:17:54.880
I just looked it up online.

00:17:55.000 --> 00:17:56.519
Given Dad's current condition,

00:17:56.519 --> 00:17:57.599
look what it says online.

00:17:58.680 --> 00:18:00.720
A conflict of psychic functions

00:18:00.720 --> 00:18:03.240
caused his psychological defense mechanisms

00:18:03.240 --> 00:18:05.359
to activate, stirring up the

00:18:05.359 --> 00:18:06.440
irreconcilable conflict between his id and superego.

00:18:06.440 --> 00:18:07.240
So you're saying...

00:18:07.559 --> 00:18:09.680
Son, explain it in plain language.

00:18:09.759 --> 00:18:11.279
In plain terms, it means

00:18:12.200 --> 00:18:13.279
he's had a shock.

00:18:13.279 --> 00:18:14.559
No, you kid, you...

00:18:14.559 --> 00:18:16.440
Mom, let me tell you.

00:18:17.359 --> 00:18:18.839
Third Uncle did this on purpose.

00:18:19.960 --> 00:18:21.279
He told me a couple days ago

00:18:21.319 --> 00:18:23.720
he wants to shake Dad out of it,

00:18:23.720 --> 00:18:25.880
to get back his old "Baofang Boss" spirit.

00:18:34.759 --> 00:18:36.119
What you did,

00:18:36.519 --> 00:18:37.519
your intention was good.

00:18:37.519 --> 00:18:39.240
But your methods were

00:18:39.240 --> 00:18:40.440
a bit too extreme.

00:18:41.200 --> 00:18:42.200
No choice.

00:18:42.319 --> 00:18:44.039
A severe illness needs strong medicine.

00:18:45.279 --> 00:18:47.799
But Uncle Wang isn't your subordinate.

00:18:47.920 --> 00:18:49.880
He's the leader of the Baofang Brothers.

00:18:49.880 --> 00:18:51.200
And Wang Fei's father.

00:18:51.200 --> 00:18:53.200
He has his own pride and dignity.

00:18:54.519 --> 00:18:55.759
You're so young,

00:18:56.000 --> 00:18:57.960
talking like you've seen it all.

00:18:58.799 --> 00:19:01.200
I'm just an objective observer.

00:19:16.480 --> 00:19:17.680
You're finally here!

00:19:17.680 --> 00:19:18.720
Come in, quick.

00:19:20.680 --> 00:19:21.480
I'll get it.

00:19:26.839 --> 00:19:29.279
Sister-in-law, how's Big Brother doing?

00:19:30.839 --> 00:19:31.680
Weiguo,

00:19:31.680 --> 00:19:34.680
I don't care what your plan is,

00:19:34.920 --> 00:19:36.880
but what you said yesterday was too hurtful.

00:19:36.880 --> 00:19:38.880
You always hit right where it hurts.

00:19:38.880 --> 00:19:39.880
That's not right, is it?

00:19:40.359 --> 00:19:42.400
He hasn't said a single decent word since he got back.

00:19:42.680 --> 00:19:44.079
I really didn't expect

00:19:44.079 --> 00:19:46.039
him to be so tactless.

00:19:46.440 --> 00:19:48.440
You really hurt your Big Brother.

00:19:49.000 --> 00:19:50.279
Go in and see him.

00:19:50.599 --> 00:19:51.200
Alright.

00:19:52.640 --> 00:19:53.440
Over there.

00:20:05.319 --> 00:20:06.240
Big Brother.

00:20:31.119 --> 00:20:31.799
Big Brother.

00:20:33.359 --> 00:20:34.319
I know I was wrong.

00:20:35.599 --> 00:20:36.920
I actually meant well,

00:20:38.039 --> 00:20:39.279
I just went too far.

00:20:39.480 --> 00:20:40.359
I'm sorry.

00:20:42.920 --> 00:20:44.480
Big Brother, look,

00:20:44.799 --> 00:20:46.079
he knows he was wrong.

00:20:46.119 --> 00:20:47.680
Just calm down, okay?

00:20:50.359 --> 00:20:50.920
No.

00:20:52.359 --> 00:20:54.359
No, if you're really that angry,

00:20:54.359 --> 00:20:55.519
just give him a beating.

00:20:55.519 --> 00:20:56.960
This kid can take a punch anyway.

00:20:57.200 --> 00:20:58.640
Don't worry about my feelings.

00:20:58.920 --> 00:20:59.599
Okay?

00:21:36.960 --> 00:21:37.680
So?

00:21:37.680 --> 00:21:38.240
What's the situation?

00:21:38.240 --> 00:21:40.160
I see the food on Big Brother's table is untouched.

00:21:40.160 --> 00:21:41.279
Has he not eaten at all?

00:21:41.279 --> 00:21:43.680
Exactly! I'm worried sick.

00:21:44.359 --> 00:21:46.200
I remember Big Brother loves chive pockets.

00:21:46.200 --> 00:21:47.000
How about this:

00:21:47.000 --> 00:21:48.960
Sister-in-law, go downstairs and buy a few.

00:21:49.000 --> 00:21:50.000
Fresh out of the pan.

00:21:50.599 --> 00:21:52.160
Why didn't I think of that?

00:21:52.160 --> 00:21:54.079
No, what do you mean?

00:21:54.240 --> 00:21:55.240
Big Brother is in this state,

00:21:55.240 --> 00:21:56.279
and you want to buy chive pockets?

00:21:56.279 --> 00:21:57.400
Who are you celebrating for?

00:21:58.400 --> 00:22:00.559
I have an idea, but don't say it's mean.

00:22:01.000 --> 00:22:02.559
I don't care how mean it is.

00:22:02.559 --> 00:22:03.960
As long as it cures him.

00:22:03.960 --> 00:22:04.680
I'll go get them now.

00:22:04.680 --> 00:22:05.519
Thanks, Sister-in-law.

00:22:08.559 --> 00:22:09.319
Later on,

00:22:09.480 --> 00:22:10.799
let's work together.

00:22:16.720 --> 00:22:19.559
Smells amazing. So good.

00:22:27.680 --> 00:22:28.680
You know,

00:22:29.119 --> 00:22:31.519
if a person could go without eating or drinking,

00:22:31.519 --> 00:22:33.200
wouldn't they become an immortal?

00:22:33.880 --> 00:22:35.079
Even if he were an immortal,

00:22:35.079 --> 00:22:36.720
he'd know how delicious these chive pockets are.

00:22:36.720 --> 00:22:37.359
Yeah.

00:22:37.799 --> 00:22:38.559
Look at this.

00:22:38.680 --> 00:22:40.440
The golden crust, the green filling.

00:22:40.799 --> 00:22:41.759
So fragrant.

00:22:41.759 --> 00:22:43.519
Bite into it, and the juices flow.

00:22:43.599 --> 00:22:45.079
Even Lü Dongbin himself,

00:22:45.079 --> 00:22:46.160
would have to open wide

00:22:46.160 --> 00:22:47.160
and eat five or six of them.

00:22:47.160 --> 00:22:49.799
Yeah, smells so good, really good.

00:22:51.599 --> 00:22:54.039
So good, so good, so good.

00:22:57.920 --> 00:22:59.680
So good, so good.

00:23:15.160 --> 00:23:17.920
Lianbao, do you smell that?

00:23:17.920 --> 00:23:18.839
What smell?

00:23:21.960 --> 00:23:24.240
I smell it. What is that?

00:23:24.920 --> 00:23:25.720
Seriously.

00:23:27.240 --> 00:23:28.279
I know.

00:23:28.759 --> 00:23:30.920
See why Big Brother is under the covers?

00:23:30.920 --> 00:23:31.519
Yeah.

00:23:31.519 --> 00:23:33.200
Big Brother must have wet the bed.

00:23:34.039 --> 00:23:35.680
Big Brother wet the bed!

00:23:35.680 --> 00:23:36.720
And he's covering it with the blanket

00:23:36.720 --> 00:23:37.839
so he doesn't stink up the place for us.

00:23:38.079 --> 00:23:38.680
See?

00:23:38.680 --> 00:23:40.680
Why did he bury his head in there?

00:23:41.000 --> 00:23:42.160
He wants

00:23:42.160 --> 00:23:44.119
to inhale all the smell himself

00:23:44.119 --> 00:23:45.519
to avoid polluting the environment.

00:23:45.519 --> 00:23:47.119
How noble of him!

00:23:47.319 --> 00:23:49.000
Big Brother still cares about us.

00:23:49.759 --> 00:23:52.039
You little brat, how mean can you be?

00:23:52.279 --> 00:23:53.440
So I'm in bed,

00:23:53.440 --> 00:23:54.319
eating and relieving myself in bed,

00:23:54.319 --> 00:23:56.000
and popping popcorn in bed too?

00:23:56.279 --> 00:23:57.160
Get out!

00:23:58.000 --> 00:23:59.079
Out, out, out!

00:23:59.079 --> 00:24:00.319
Get out! Out!

00:24:02.359 --> 00:24:03.119
Out!

00:24:20.720 --> 00:24:21.400
You know what,

00:24:22.279 --> 00:24:23.519
if we had some vinegar

00:24:23.680 --> 00:24:25.240
and a clove of garlic, it'd be perfect.

00:24:26.599 --> 00:24:28.480
Big Brother, smells good, right?

00:24:28.480 --> 00:24:28.920
It really does smell good.

00:24:28.920 --> 00:24:30.440
Get out! Scram!

00:24:31.079 --> 00:24:32.279
Get out!

00:24:33.559 --> 00:24:35.519
You saw how Big Brother was just now?

00:24:36.160 --> 00:24:37.160
I was afraid if I said more,

00:24:37.160 --> 00:24:38.359
he'd start swinging.

00:24:38.640 --> 00:24:40.079
Your trick was really mean.

00:24:40.079 --> 00:24:42.440
At least he's willing to get out of bed now.

00:24:46.079 --> 00:24:46.559
No.

00:24:46.559 --> 00:24:47.240
What's wrong?

00:24:48.440 --> 00:24:50.279
It's nothing. My blood sugar's a bit low.

00:24:50.680 --> 00:24:51.559
Should we go to the hospital?

00:24:51.559 --> 00:24:52.680
What hospital?

00:24:55.279 --> 00:24:58.759
I think if Big Brother practices his skills now,

00:24:59.240 --> 00:25:00.279
there's still enough time.

00:25:01.160 --> 00:25:02.720
Don't worry about this.

00:25:02.720 --> 00:25:03.960
Trust me, I'm right.

00:25:07.279 --> 00:25:08.519
Are you really okay or not?

00:25:08.519 --> 00:25:09.279
I'm fine.

00:25:09.759 --> 00:25:11.160
Just need something sweet.

00:25:16.880 --> 00:25:17.519
No.

00:25:18.400 --> 00:25:20.200
Can you not block the TV?

00:25:33.319 --> 00:25:33.799
No.

00:25:34.920 --> 00:25:37.640
I'm saying, how did you mop the floor like this?

00:25:38.359 --> 00:25:40.559
Can't you see how dirty it is here?

00:25:41.599 --> 00:25:43.200
No, I cleaned every nook and cranny.

00:25:43.200 --> 00:25:45.200
Look over there, how dirty it is. Look.

00:25:47.359 --> 00:25:49.200
No, what are you doing here?

00:25:49.480 --> 00:25:50.680
If you're going to eat, eat properly.

00:25:50.680 --> 00:25:51.599
Put your phone down.

00:25:54.000 --> 00:25:55.599
Finish your meal and go do your homework.

00:25:55.960 --> 00:25:57.160
Already finished it.

00:25:57.720 --> 00:25:59.400
Finished, so you think you're in the right?

00:25:59.920 --> 00:26:01.480
Don't you know exams are coming up?

00:26:01.480 --> 00:26:03.200
Go over all the key points again.

00:26:04.240 --> 00:26:04.920
Fine.

00:26:10.160 --> 00:26:11.720
How did you wipe this table?

00:26:11.720 --> 00:26:13.480
Can't you see all these fingerprints?

00:26:13.920 --> 00:26:15.039
Look. Come here and look.

00:26:15.039 --> 00:26:15.799
Look.

00:26:17.559 --> 00:26:20.119
No, you need to stop now.

00:26:20.920 --> 00:26:22.160
Are you eating or not?

00:26:22.160 --> 00:26:23.160
Not hungry.

00:26:23.880 --> 00:26:26.720
If you're not hungry, then go back to your room and lie down.

00:26:40.559 --> 00:26:42.759
No, I told you to sharpen this knife for me.

00:26:42.759 --> 00:26:44.039
Didn't you hear me?

00:26:44.960 --> 00:26:46.359
Wang Chunsheng, let me tell you.

00:26:46.359 --> 00:26:47.559
If I sharpen this knife,

00:26:47.559 --> 00:26:49.079
I'll slaughter you with it.

00:26:54.519 --> 00:26:55.680
No, this kitchen floor...

00:26:55.680 --> 00:26:56.440
We just finished cooking.

00:26:56.440 --> 00:26:58.079
Can you clean it up first?

00:26:58.079 --> 00:27:00.359
Is this how responsible people live?

00:27:01.279 --> 00:27:03.599
What, are we giving up on this life?

00:27:11.039 --> 00:27:12.160
Hurry up!

00:27:20.200 --> 00:27:21.000
Dad sees this and thinks,

00:27:21.000 --> 00:27:22.200
His illness isn't better yet.

00:27:25.200 --> 00:27:26.359
Before it was stillness,

00:27:26.359 --> 00:27:28.079
now it's turned into mania.

00:27:28.079 --> 00:27:28.920
Yeah.

00:27:29.039 --> 00:27:29.839
He's gone from one extreme

00:27:29.839 --> 00:27:31.200
to the other.

00:27:34.759 --> 00:27:35.599
Martin.

00:27:35.839 --> 00:27:38.480
Based on the symptoms you described,

00:27:38.480 --> 00:27:42.000
it should be the glioma lesion

00:27:42.440 --> 00:27:45.440
compressing the optic nerve.

00:27:46.400 --> 00:27:48.440
Martin, this is very dangerous if it continues.

00:27:48.440 --> 00:27:50.799
Please come back as soon as possible for a full examination.

00:27:50.799 --> 00:27:53.279
Only then can I understand the lesion's progression.

00:27:54.680 --> 00:27:56.599
I can't return in the short term.

00:27:59.279 --> 00:28:00.240
Martin.

00:28:00.359 --> 00:28:03.480
What could be more important than life?

00:28:04.599 --> 00:28:07.200
Are you still not considering the surgical option?

00:28:09.240 --> 00:28:09.920
No.

00:28:10.119 --> 00:28:10.759
Thank you.

00:28:11.599 --> 00:28:12.400
Goodbye.

00:28:15.599 --> 00:28:16.480
Martin?

00:28:34.200 --> 00:28:35.079
What's up?

00:28:36.519 --> 00:28:37.200
Are you busy?

00:28:37.680 --> 00:28:38.799
Should I come back later?

00:28:38.960 --> 00:28:40.920
No, you finally came.

00:28:40.920 --> 00:28:42.160
It must be something important.

00:28:42.160 --> 00:28:42.759
Speak.

00:28:47.039 --> 00:28:48.319
Forget it, I won't tease you.

00:28:49.119 --> 00:28:50.000
What is it?

00:28:50.000 --> 00:28:50.799
I know.

00:28:51.240 --> 00:28:52.359
It's about Uncle Wang, right?

00:28:54.119 --> 00:28:54.720
Yes.

00:28:57.759 --> 00:28:58.920
I just wanted to...

00:28:59.240 --> 00:29:00.920
Your emotional intelligence is pretty high, right?

00:29:01.400 --> 00:29:03.240
What should I do now

00:29:03.799 --> 00:29:05.680
to make up for the hurt I caused Big Brother?

00:29:10.359 --> 00:29:12.000
Doesn't he have a motorcycle?

00:29:12.440 --> 00:29:13.920
I think you could surprise him.

00:29:13.920 --> 00:29:16.279
Give him a gift related to motorcycles.

00:29:17.799 --> 00:29:19.480
Two grown men giving each other gifts...

00:29:19.480 --> 00:29:21.440
Wouldn't that be a bit corny?

00:29:21.920 --> 00:29:22.960
How could it be?

00:29:23.160 --> 00:29:24.599
Do what you want to do.

00:29:24.599 --> 00:29:26.000
What does being a man or woman have to do with it?

00:29:26.000 --> 00:29:27.680
Just express your sincerity.

00:29:27.960 --> 00:29:29.880
But every time I want to do something,

00:29:30.000 --> 00:29:31.359
it ends up hurting people.

00:29:31.799 --> 00:29:32.799
You know it too.

00:29:34.119 --> 00:29:35.000
I've heard.

00:29:38.680 --> 00:29:39.559
Give it a try.

00:29:42.039 --> 00:29:42.680
Alright.

00:29:43.680 --> 00:29:44.359
Thanks.

00:29:44.359 --> 00:29:45.200
You're welcome.

00:30:02.200 --> 00:30:03.599
As for Wang Xiaoai's side,

00:30:03.599 --> 00:30:05.599
the situation looks quite threatening.

00:30:05.599 --> 00:30:06.920
This might require us to

00:30:06.920 --> 00:30:08.039
pay more attention then.

00:30:09.759 --> 00:30:12.480
And then, that Master Cao from the duck shop,

00:30:12.480 --> 00:30:13.759
his skills are also very strong.

00:30:13.880 --> 00:30:15.799
We can observe him more closely then.

00:30:16.039 --> 00:30:18.119
Anyway, that's basically the situation.

00:30:18.119 --> 00:30:19.039
Nothing else.

00:30:19.519 --> 00:30:20.079
Okay.

00:30:36.680 --> 00:30:38.720
You rushed here in such a hurry to see me,

00:30:38.720 --> 00:30:40.039
and now you're not saying anything.

00:30:46.880 --> 00:30:47.920
As for me,

00:30:48.240 --> 00:30:49.960
I just wanted to explain something.

00:30:51.039 --> 00:30:53.119
I must sign Master Sun.

00:30:53.400 --> 00:30:54.759
I really need him.

00:30:57.440 --> 00:30:58.599
We each rely on our own abilities.

00:31:00.119 --> 00:31:01.400
You won this round.

00:31:01.599 --> 00:31:02.759
I have nothing to say.

00:31:10.000 --> 00:31:10.720
Qianqian.

00:31:11.599 --> 00:31:12.839
Are you angry?

00:31:14.640 --> 00:31:16.039
You're overthinking it.

00:31:16.759 --> 00:31:18.039
Is there anything else?

00:31:18.160 --> 00:31:19.240
If not, you can leave.

00:31:23.160 --> 00:31:24.599
How about we cooperate?

00:31:26.200 --> 00:31:26.880
Think about it.

00:31:26.880 --> 00:31:28.640
This isn't just good for the two of us.

00:31:29.119 --> 00:31:31.119
It's good for Big Brother, for Qiu'er, for everyone.

00:31:32.079 --> 00:31:32.920
Furthermore,

00:31:33.119 --> 00:31:35.680
all of us grew up together.

00:31:36.599 --> 00:31:38.279
Don't you care about them at all?

00:31:38.680 --> 00:31:41.000
I care about them in other ways.

00:31:41.519 --> 00:31:42.200
What?

00:31:42.720 --> 00:31:44.480
Do I have to drag them into a partnership together

00:31:44.480 --> 00:31:45.839
for it to count as caring?

00:31:48.200 --> 00:31:49.240
It's you.

00:31:50.200 --> 00:31:52.359
You always mix business with personal feelings.

00:31:52.359 --> 00:31:53.000
Because of that,

00:31:53.000 --> 00:31:54.279
I don't want to cooperate with you.

00:31:54.599 --> 00:31:56.839
No, I can tell the difference when it matters.

00:32:02.160 --> 00:32:03.279
If you don't believe me,

00:32:03.279 --> 00:32:04.279
there's nothing I can do.

00:32:04.519 --> 00:32:06.359
But I must succeed in this.

00:32:06.519 --> 00:32:07.480
You'll see.

00:32:10.400 --> 00:32:11.279
Lianbao.

00:32:12.160 --> 00:32:13.759
There are many ways

00:32:13.920 --> 00:32:15.039
to achieve success.

00:32:15.839 --> 00:32:17.160
I don't think you need to put

00:32:17.160 --> 00:32:18.359
such a heavy burden on yourself.

00:32:19.440 --> 00:32:20.599
You're not their brother,

00:32:20.599 --> 00:32:21.839
so of course you don't understand.

00:32:26.039 --> 00:32:27.440
When that incident happened,

00:32:28.000 --> 00:32:29.799
Ma Weiguo just up and left.

00:32:29.880 --> 00:32:31.200
He only came back after all these years.

00:32:33.359 --> 00:32:34.839
When Big Brother got out of prison,

00:32:35.400 --> 00:32:37.160
he lost all his authority.

00:32:37.680 --> 00:32:40.240
And Qiu'er? He never shoulders any responsibility.

00:32:40.519 --> 00:32:41.759
So what could I do?

00:32:41.839 --> 00:32:43.599
I had to step up and be the leader.

00:32:45.279 --> 00:32:46.799
I'm the second brother.

00:32:46.880 --> 00:32:49.160
I shouldn't have to deal with any of this.

00:32:52.720 --> 00:32:54.119
But if I don't,

00:32:55.359 --> 00:32:56.839
the brothers will truly fall apart.

00:33:00.200 --> 00:33:01.200
You could do this:

00:33:02.039 --> 00:33:03.799
hand Peng Le Xuan over to me.

00:33:04.000 --> 00:33:06.160
I'll make proper arrangements for each of you.

00:33:06.160 --> 00:33:07.039
Impossible.

00:33:08.039 --> 00:33:10.160
Then I'd really be letting Big Brother down for life.

00:33:14.440 --> 00:33:15.039
Fine.

00:33:16.480 --> 00:33:17.839
Is there anything else?

00:33:18.279 --> 00:33:19.359
You really should leave now.

00:33:27.319 --> 00:33:28.200
Qianqian.

00:33:28.880 --> 00:33:30.240
Please reconsider.

00:33:31.640 --> 00:33:32.599
I won't see you out.

00:33:52.680 --> 00:33:53.640
I'm sorry.

00:33:54.640 --> 00:33:55.720
I can't lose.

00:36:30.760 --> 00:36:31.519
What are you doing?

00:36:31.519 --> 00:36:32.840
Don't you touch my motorcycle!

00:36:33.639 --> 00:36:35.000
No, I, I...

00:36:35.000 --> 00:36:36.119
I... I was trying to...

00:36:36.239 --> 00:36:37.199
What were you trying to do?

00:36:38.039 --> 00:36:39.440
I know what you're thinking.

00:36:39.719 --> 00:36:41.480
You think I can't even raise my own son properly.

00:36:41.480 --> 00:36:42.239
Right?

00:36:42.519 --> 00:36:44.360
My roast duck isn't that great either.

00:36:44.360 --> 00:36:45.000
Right?

00:36:45.239 --> 00:36:46.519
And I'm no good at being

00:36:46.519 --> 00:36:47.800
some lousy Chairman, right?

00:36:47.800 --> 00:36:49.679
And now you dare touch my motorcycle?

00:36:49.679 --> 00:36:50.800
What's wrong with you?

00:36:52.280 --> 00:36:54.199
You're not happy when I work.

00:36:54.320 --> 00:36:55.840
You're not happy when I do nothing.

00:36:55.840 --> 00:36:57.119
You come to my house to disgust me.

00:36:57.119 --> 00:36:59.239
Are you unhappy even when I breathe?

00:37:00.119 --> 00:37:01.119
Uncle Wang.

00:37:01.719 --> 00:37:03.280
Uncle Wang, you've misunderstood.

00:37:03.280 --> 00:37:04.719
Uncle Ma got new parts for you.

00:37:04.719 --> 00:37:06.320
He wanted to upgrade your bike.

00:37:08.079 --> 00:37:08.840
Careful, careful!

00:37:10.559 --> 00:37:12.239
Don't give me that routine!

00:37:12.400 --> 00:37:13.679
You think I'm a three-year-old?

00:37:13.679 --> 00:37:14.639
Hit me, then rub it better?

00:37:14.639 --> 00:37:15.920
Offer me a couple of sweet dates?

00:37:18.519 --> 00:37:19.880
Uncle Wang, Uncle Ma's hand is covered in blood.

00:37:19.880 --> 00:37:20.679
Don't say anymore.

00:37:22.719 --> 00:37:23.400
Let's go.

00:37:59.599 --> 00:38:00.639
Sometimes I really don't understand

00:38:00.639 --> 00:38:02.039
what you men are thinking.

00:38:04.440 --> 00:38:05.320
If you have something to say,

00:38:06.480 --> 00:38:08.239
why not just say it directly?

00:38:12.119 --> 00:38:12.440
Gently.

00:38:12.440 --> 00:38:12.840
Bear with it.

00:38:13.599 --> 00:38:14.199
Be gentle.

00:38:14.199 --> 00:38:14.760
Okay.

00:38:20.320 --> 00:38:21.000
Does it hurt?

00:38:24.920 --> 00:38:26.760
I just wanted to help him get back on his feet.

00:38:27.320 --> 00:38:28.800
I didn't mean to put on a sob story.

00:38:29.599 --> 00:38:31.840
It just proves your trick didn't work.

00:38:33.840 --> 00:38:34.880
Stubborn.

00:38:40.239 --> 00:38:41.679
Gently, slowly.

00:38:44.599 --> 00:38:46.360
So you *do* know it hurts?

00:38:46.519 --> 00:38:47.400
Of course.

00:38:51.840 --> 00:38:53.320
It looks painful.

00:38:54.559 --> 00:38:55.360
Done?

00:38:59.320 --> 00:39:00.800
Okay, wait a second.

00:39:03.880 --> 00:39:04.599
Don't shake it.

00:39:20.719 --> 00:39:21.400
There.

00:39:23.480 --> 00:39:24.280
Thanks.

00:39:26.280 --> 00:39:27.000
You're welcome.

00:39:42.599 --> 00:39:43.440
Excuse me.

00:39:43.519 --> 00:39:45.599
Could you help me return this, please?

00:39:45.719 --> 00:39:46.559
Thank you.

00:39:48.639 --> 00:39:50.679
I just bought it the day before yesterday, never used it.

00:40:00.880 --> 00:40:02.239
I'm sorry, sir.

00:40:02.239 --> 00:40:03.880
This bag is not from our store.

00:40:11.000 --> 00:40:12.199
But the receipt says your store.

00:40:12.199 --> 00:40:13.639
How is it not? This...

00:40:14.360 --> 00:40:16.880
How is this bag I bought myself not from here?

00:40:17.280 --> 00:40:18.360
Take another look.

00:40:18.440 --> 00:40:19.920
It's definitely from your store.

00:40:19.920 --> 00:40:21.599
When did you come to buy it?

00:40:21.719 --> 00:40:23.480
Did you come buy this bag yourself?

00:40:25.920 --> 00:40:27.920
A friend of mine came to buy it.

00:40:28.079 --> 00:40:29.199
Please look again.

00:40:31.119 --> 00:40:32.639
The receipt is genuine,

00:40:32.880 --> 00:40:34.719
but this is absolutely not our store's bag.

00:40:42.880 --> 00:40:45.719
Honey, I'm catching an early flight, leaving now.

00:40:46.920 --> 00:40:49.079
Text me when you get to the airport.

00:40:53.039 --> 00:40:53.840
The bag...

00:41:06.800 --> 00:41:07.480
I...

00:41:08.039 --> 00:41:09.880
This... I'm so sorry.

00:41:10.320 --> 00:41:11.400
I took the wrong one.

00:41:12.199 --> 00:41:14.280
You can mix up a bag worth tens of thousands?

00:41:14.280 --> 00:41:16.239
If you're going to lie, make it believable.

00:41:16.360 --> 00:41:17.159
Manager!

00:41:18.599 --> 00:41:19.880
Xiaofeng, what's going on?

00:41:20.119 --> 00:41:22.039
This person brought a fake bag to return.

00:41:22.039 --> 00:41:22.880
No, no, no!

00:41:22.880 --> 00:41:24.039
There's a bit of a misunderstanding.

00:41:24.039 --> 00:41:25.000
Yes, how do I explain...

00:41:25.000 --> 00:41:25.840
My bag...

00:41:25.840 --> 00:41:28.039
I... I left it at home.

00:41:28.239 --> 00:41:29.639
No, I left...

00:41:29.639 --> 00:41:31.599
Okay, okay, um, I...

00:41:31.760 --> 00:41:32.519
No, like this.

00:41:32.519 --> 00:41:33.519
I'll leave this bag here as collateral.

00:41:33.519 --> 00:41:35.159
I'll bring you the real bag, okay?

00:41:35.159 --> 00:41:35.920
Don't you leave.

00:41:37.760 --> 00:41:39.760
No, this, this... really, there's...

00:41:39.760 --> 00:41:41.920
If you... if you don't believe me, then I'll have to...

00:41:41.920 --> 00:41:43.039
Otherwise... otherwise I'll call... call the police.

00:41:43.039 --> 00:41:45.360
Let the... police officers clear... clear my name.

00:41:45.360 --> 00:41:46.440
How about this?

00:41:49.599 --> 00:41:50.480
I'll call them myself.